{"tid":380731,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"依家d 90後成個大種乞衣咁，公司拎去destroy既野都乞！","createTime":"2017-08-30T11:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T09:49:11.000Z","uid":19334,"like":13,"dislike":194,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9eb0557689e529582f291c0868b884ac3c5d29","tid":380731,"uid":19334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:00:37.000Z","msg":"話說公司呢排開Party，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁有一次就係叫到會既（公司請），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我叫左兩兜雞翼，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我預大家都會食（我一個人食到一兜），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁其他人就叫左炒米炒飯Pizza etc，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知開完P，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n執番個地方果陣時，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n竟然發現到另一兜雞翼竟然開都無開過！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我咪準備dun左佢（食到好飽了），<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻90後竟然問可唔可以拎番屋企！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我心入面打左突，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘩洗唔洗乞衣成咁先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n連果兜雞翼都貪！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca83e0c0c5f47acd6a50848730834f6da74bccb9","tid":380731,"uid":128219,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:01:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1ceb465579445e1f98bf4248a73959fbd6a6b69","tid":380731,"uid":32899,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"樓豬好波"},{"pid":"ae5a8fa55aca83bf7f4c72de874935ba40150954","tid":380731,"ui